data.title: Amr Kashmiri
data.meta_description: Amr Saleem Kashmiri is a Pakistani-born actor and Film Editor who appears in Pakistani films. He made his film debut in 2011 with Shoaib Mansoor's Bol for which he won a London Asian Film Festival award.
